{"tid":1448913,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:42:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:07:40.000Z","uid":143355,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a45ed53184b7ab542ee3618662b834860a8bb200","tid":1448913,"uid":143355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:42:47.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvBZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=bb7f9e69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvBZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=60447324\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"62b67721bcf259c57cae54bdba2ae79cd702fc3d","tid":1448913,"uid":114882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:43:25.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"73e472bed21b64ab017ff0bb8cad98a29a1ffcf2","tid":1448913,"uid":114882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:44:07.000Z","msg":"警察還眼"},{"pid":"181258a0382605d386fd1d4faa987ab650bb6fc3","tid":1448913,"uid":143355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:44:43.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"c32d3c4922bc5bbfbea25824550d073e64c84663","tid":1448913,"uid":182794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:45